video.title: Wentworth
video.synopsis: Bea Smith is locked up while awaiting trial for the alleged attempted murder of her husband and must learn how life works in prison.

episodes.synopsis: Bea Smith's sentence at Wentworth begins as she sides with tough girl Franky's gang and gets caught up in a riot that leaves the prison governor dead.
episodes.title: No Place Like Home

episodes.synopsis: Harry thwarts Bea's attempts to contact her daughter, and Meg's husband hunts for her killer. Meanwhile, a power struggle leaves Vera humiliated.
episodes.title: Fly Me Away

episodes.synopsis: Franky's estranged father visits, and Bea is caught in Jacs and Franky's rivalry. Meanwhile, Erica attempts to change how Wentworth is run.
episodes.title: The Girl Who Waited

episodes.synopsis: Franky retaliates against Bea's breach of loyalty, and Liz botches a VIP event when she relapses. Meanwhile, Jacs learns of her husband's affair.
episodes.title: The Things We Do

episodes.synopsis: An erotic dream makes Erica uncomfortable with being Franky's tutor, and her growing sexual issues start to affect her relationship with Mark.
episodes.title: The Velvet Curtain

episodes.synopsis: Vera's attempts to assert herself backfire with Fletch and her own mother, and Jacs forces Toni to tell Erica that Franky gave her drugs.
episodes.title: Captive

episodes.synopsis: Jacs has Wentworth in the palm of her hand, and she has a vicious surprise waiting for Franky, who's about to be released back into the compound.
episodes.title: Something Dies

episodes.synopsis: As Bea's popularity grows, Jacs is backed into a corner. She blackmails Will, claims Vera caused Meg's death and plans a final move against her rival.
episodes.title: Mind Games

episodes.synopsis: Bea's grief over her daughter's death is compounded when she is forbidden to attend the funeral. Meanwhile, Jacs triggers her last attack against Bea.
episodes.title: To The Moon

episodes.synopsis: Bea believes Jacs was behind her daughter's death. Meanwhile, Fletch and Vera reconcile, but she comes to believe that he killed Meg.
episodes.title: Checkmate

episodes.synopsis: Hoping to end Franky's stranglehold on Wentworth, new governor Joan Ferguson breaks up her contraband operation and brings Bea back to H Block.
episodes.title: Born Again

episodes.synopsis: Bea agrees to Harry's request for a divorce on the condition that he kill Brayden Holt. Meanwhile, Franky tries to get heroin from a new drug mule.
episodes.title: Whatever It Takes

episodes.synopsis: Brayden Holt's godmother returns to Wentworth, giving Bea hope for revenge. But Franky is troubled by her arrival, as she once worked for Jacs.
episodes.title: Boys In The Yard

episodes.synopsis: Bea learns of the Holts' plan to avenge Brayden and asks Franky to get her a weapon. But the attempts on her life come from an unexpected source.
episodes.title: The Danger Within

episodes.synopsis: Bea uses the news that Simmo's daughter is working for the Holts to her advantage. Meanwhile, Wentworth is turned upside down when Boomer vanishes.
episodes.title: Twist The Knife

episodes.synopsis: Simmo can't bring herself to kill Bea and attempts suicide, only to be saved by Bea. Meanwhile, Ferguson makes use of Franky's illicit drugs.
episodes.title: The Pink Dragon

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson cancels the garden project, Maxine tries to escape when she learns Gary is headed overseas and Franky confronts Ferguson over Simmo's death.
episodes.title: Metamorphosis

episodes.synopsis: Franky is determined to find the snitch in Wentworth, and her evidence points to Bea, who's getting special privileges.
episodes.title: Sins Of The Mother

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson attempts to force Doreen into a lie about the father of her baby. Meanwhile, Will feuds with Harry, who he thinks has been harassing him.
episodes.title: The Fixer

episodes.synopsis: Liz is released from Wentworth but finds life at the halfway house difficult, especially when Boomer threatens to have her attacked.
episodes.title: Jail Birds

episodes.synopsis: The battle lines are drawn between Bea and Franky for domination of Wentworth, and Fletch believes a new inmate may be his key to ousting Ferguson.
episodes.title: Into The Night

episodes.synopsis: Bea flees the hospital and sets out to avenge Debbie's death, Fletch tries to warn Will about Ferguson and Liz prepares to return to Wentworth.
episodes.title: Fear Her

episodes.synopsis: After Bea is sentenced to life without parole, Ferguson believes she has the upper hand. But a battle for control of the prison soon breaks out.
episodes.title: The Governor's Pleasure

episodes.synopsis: In an attempt to secure her position as the prison's top dog, Bea engages in a delicate and dangerous alliance with Ferguson.
episodes.title: Failing Upwards

episodes.synopsis: With her supply line cut and her power base destroyed, Franky is in trouble with prisoners she owes. Meanwhile, Bea is shocked by Will's confession.
episodes.title: Knives Out

episodes.synopsis: A new prisoner, unprepared for the tough world of Wentworth, shocks Liz. Franky makes a startling confession to Bridget, and Bea is attacked.
episodes.title: Righteous Act

episodes.synopsis: Fletch has a tough time readjusting to work, while Bea makes a secret plan to take down Ferguson and has a disturbing visitor.
episodes.title: Mercy

episodes.synopsis: Jodie's complaint to the ombudsman blindsides Ferguson, who figures out that Bea is behind it and seeks a brutal revenge.
episodes.title: Evidence

episodes.synopsis: Bea has trouble accepting that she had a psychotic episode, but realizes that it means she'll have to play the long game to defeat Ferguson.
episodes.title: The Long Game

episodes.synopsis: Bea enlists Doreen to uncover why Ferguson is obsessed with someone named "Jianna," but that triggers Ferguson's renewed interest in Doreen.
episodes.title: Goldfish

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson angles to remove her most ardent accuser, while Bea hits a low point after realizing the heavy toll her war with Ferguson is taking.
episodes.title: Freak Show

episodes.synopsis: Franky faces a tricky situation when her parole hearing is moved up, and Doreen must make a difficult decision regarding her baby.
episodes.title: A Higher Court

episodes.synopsis: Using her alliance with Fletch, Bea drives a wedge between Ferguson and Vera, but it sets off an unstoppable chain of events.
episodes.title: The Living and The Dead

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson is losing control and Fletch and Vera band together to overthrow her, while Bea discovers the final piece of the puzzle in Harry's murder.
episodes.title: Blood and Fire

episodes.synopsis: Fire-damaged H Block reopens, but a shift in power and new adversaries make Bea wonder if she's up to the task of remaining Top Dog.
episodes.title: First Blood

episodes.synopsis: Vera forms an unusual alliance with Bridget and Franky to expose Ferguson. Kaz leads a protest demanding conjugal visits.
episodes.title: Poking Spiders

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson returns to the general population, and Vera protects her by confining her to her cell while wondering what Ferguson is planning.
episodes.title: Prisoner

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson earns Kaz's respect when she claims that Will beat her and is sleeping with Bea, who's branded a "screw lover" for coming to Will's defense.
episodes.title: Screw Lover

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson uses Kaz's emotional fragility to manipulate her into acting against Bea and intervening in a new inmate's skirmish with Lucy.
episodes.title: Love and Hate

episodes.synopsis: When Bea returns, Lucy accosts her and demands that she punish a rule-breaking inmate. Doreen rejects Bea and Liz looks after a new inmate.
episodes.title: Divide and Conquer

episodes.synopsis: Bea holds a vote among the inmates to determine her position in the prison. Ferguson is shaken by the discovery that Bea will testify for Jesper.
episodes.title: Panic Button

episodes.synopsis: A clandestine affair heats up, but neither party knows their every move is being watched. Maxine undergoes a procedure away from the prison.
episodes.title: Plan Bea

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson is released from the burn unit, Bea tries to recuperate, and Maxine finds herself in the middle of a feud when she returns to prison.
episodes.title: Afterlife

episodes.synopsis: Bea takes action against Kaz when she discovers that Allie is in trouble. Meanwhile, Franky seeks Shayne's help to expose Ferguson's plan.
episodes.title: Smitten

episodes.synopsis: When a new relationship goes public, Kaz reaches out to Tina to form an alliance. A drug shipment creates problems for Jake and several inmates.
episodes.title: Eleventh Hour

episodes.synopsis: Bea scrambles to get a step ahead of Ferguson, who's scheming as the trial approaches. Maxine continues chemotherapy. Liz believes Sonia is innocent.
episodes.title: Seeing Red

episodes.synopsis: Top dog Kaz declares a controversial rule. Vera uses a scapegoat to cover her tracks. Franky has a strange encounter with a face from her past.
episodes.title: Scars

episodes.synopsis: When shown the murder weapon, Franky recognizes it and forms a theory on who's framing her. Another inmate learns Liz is testifying against Sonia.
episodes.title: The Bitch Is Back

episodes.synopsis: While testifying in court, Liz is shaken by a new piece of evidence presented by the defense. Franky receives a letter that debunks her theory.
episodes.title: Nothing but the Truth

episodes.synopsis: With the evidence against her mounting, Franky starts to plan an escape from Wentworth. Sonia backstabs an accomplice, who turns against her.
episodes.title: Loose Ends

episodes.synopsis: An act of sabotage threatens an inmate's life. Doreen has her hearing for a transfer to Perth. Sonia returns but refuses to pay Lucy for protection.
episodes.title: Belly of the Beast

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson makes herself a hero in the inmates' eyes by creating a monster and vanquishing it. A new prison project unexpectedly allows Boomer to shine.
episodes.title: Happy Birthday, Vera

episodes.synopsis: Will develops and tests a theory on how drugs are infiltrating. Doreen gets a big surprise. After finally saving up enough heroin, Allie strikes.
episodes.title: The Pact

episodes.synopsis: Kaz and Will get a lead on which prison employee is trafficking drugs. Bridget copes poorly after being misled to think Franky is cheating on her.
episodes.title: Think Inside the Box

episodes.synopsis: Will tells Vera his suspicions about Jake. Franky asks her father for a risky favor, and later spots a familiar name on Iman's blog.
episodes.title: Snakehead

episodes.synopsis: Franky convinces Bridget to talk to Iman's psychologist. Channing learns Jake is running drugs. When another inmate is murdered, Vera is sidelined.
episodes.title: Mere Anarchy

episodes.synopsis: When Liz is accused of colluding with Sonia, she has a sinking realization. Kaz and her crew put Ferguson "on trial" in the prison yard.
episodes.title: Coup De Grce

episodes.synopsis: Franky and Allie make their escape. Liz takes a step to protect herself from Sonia. Those wronged by Ferguson decide there's only one way to stop her.
episodes.title: Hell Bent

episodes.synopsis: Franky struggles to stay one step ahead of the cops. A new inmate proves to have a shared past with another Wentworth prisoner. Vera makes a discovery.
episodes.title: Clean Slate

episodes.synopsis: Sonia returns and seeks revenge. Needing evidence, Franky targets Iman's psychologist. Ruby is forced into the fight club. Jake notices Vera's symptoms.
episodes.title: The Boxer

episodes.synopsis: Seriously wounded, Franky is forced to call Bridget, who finds a crucial lead in Iman's papers. A need for cash leads Ruby back to the fight-club ring.
episodes.title: Bleed Out

episodes.synopsis: A new inmate well-known to Allie and Kaz arrives, and offers Ruby a job. Sonia negotiates with Vera to get her workshop back. Will confesses to Jake.
episodes.title: Winter Is Here

episodes.synopsis: Vera agonizes over a decision. To improve Wentworth's image, the press are invited to the workshop. For her own reasons, Rita helps Marie get a phone.
episodes.title: Bitter Pill

episodes.synopsis: Ruby gives Boomer the support she needs to take her exam. Intel from Kaz and Will leads Vera to become suspicious of Sonia, who lures Liz into a trap.
episodes.title: Angel of Wentworth

episodes.synopsis: Liz gets the results of her medical evaluation. Sonia and Marie join forces and launch a plan to take Kaz down. Vera monitors Sonia closely on CCTV.
episodes.title: The Edge

episodes.synopsis: A stalker harasses Vera. When details of Ruby's medical condition are leaked, Allie gives her an ultimatum. Marie gets a lead on her son's killer.
episodes.title: Lovers and Fighters

episodes.synopsis: Vera discovers a link between Jake and Nils Jesper. Marie learns who's been ratting to the police and lays a trap. Liz witnesses a horrific attack.
episodes.title: Shallow Grave

episodes.synopsis: Will, Vera and Jake find themselves the victims of a blackmailer. Liz's muddled memories of the attack endanger her and cast suspicion on an innocent.
episodes.title: Fractured

episodes.synopsis: Vera and Will hunt down the suspected blackmailer. Enhanced CCTV images reveal a key clue to the identity of Danny's killer. Allie tells Marie too much.
episodes.title: Indelible Ink

episodes.synopsis: Vera meets the blackmailer alone. With Marie in the slot and Ruby about to transfer to a new prison, Drago takes matters of revenge into her own hands.
episodes.title: Showdown

episodes.synopsis: Three months pass, and Marie's court case concludes. When Ray refuses to stop pursuing her, Rita takes a risky step. Vera gets a scary wake-up call.
episodes.title: Blood Wedding

episodes.synopsis: Rita gets a tip on who was responsible for what happened to Ray. Boomer has a session with Dr. Miller, and helps Liz with an item on her bucket list.
episodes.title: Payback

episodes.synopsis: Dr. Miller forces Kaz to examine her self-destructive behavior patterns. The prison receives a new inmate with links to Rita, Allie and Kaz's pasts.
episodes.title: Atonement

episodes.synopsis: Rita desperately tries to find a way out from under Narelle's thumb. Liz has her conjugal visit. A prenatal checkup makes Vera worry.
episodes.title: Karen

episodes.synopsis: CCTV footage captures a clue to the killer's identity. Flashes of memory lead Liz to a horrifying conclusion. A vote is held for the new top dog.
episodes.title: Ascension

episodes.synopsis: Test results come back on the hoodie. Boomer is granted a day release, with her mother as her sponsor. Marie sees the note Liz has been keeping.
episodes.title: Mother

episodes.synopsis: As Ruby fights for her life at the hospital, Vera takes pity on Rita and breaks protocol. Someone else learns of Marie and Will's secret relationship.
episodes.title: Bad Blood

episodes.synopsis: A fill-in nurse in the prison infirmary makes Rita suspicious. Liz receives a visit from her son. Vera follows up on a tip about Will and Marie.
episodes.title: Protection

episodes.synopsis: Liz has a heartbreaking visit with Franky. An attempt to sneak Marie out of the prison spirals out of control, forcing Will to make a grave decision.
episodes.title: Under Siege: Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Rita finds a way to escape from the holding cell. Brody kills a second hostage. Vera goes into labor at the worst possible moment.
episodes.title: Under Siege: Part 2

episodes.synopsis: A notorious former inmate is sent back to Wentworth, testing the mettle of the new top dog.  Meanwhile, a stalker closely monitors Vera's movements.
episodes.title: Resurrection

episodes.synopsis: To get out of the prison's protective unit, Marie threatens to squeal on Will, and later reports Ruby to the police. The stalker's plan hits a snag.
episodes.title: Ends and Means

episodes.synopsis: A newly arrived activist leads the inmates in a hunger strike. Reb grows desperate to resume his hormone therapy. Ruby gets bad news from her father.
episodes.title: Enemy of the State

episodes.synopsis: Lying comatose in the hospital, the stalker is recognized by a visiting cop. To get the money for Reb's surgery, Lou sets out to kill Ruby for Marie.
episodes.title: Revenant

episodes.synopsis: Ruby enlists Judy's hacking skills to locate Rita. When someone sabotages an important presentation, Ann tasks Lou with finding out which inmate did it.
episodes.title: Fallout

episodes.synopsis: Rita launches a plan to sneak away from the safe house to rescue Ruby. Marie intervenes during an assault on Reb. Ferguson returns to Wentworth.
episodes.title: Fugitive

episodes.synopsis: Ann moves Ferguson to General. After learning she's to be extradited to the US, Judy scrambles to find a way to call her dad. Boomer meets a man.
episodes.title: Battle Lines

episodes.synopsis: To end a lockdown, Allie must find out and reveal who attacked Ann. When Dr. Miller stalls on approving Reb's surgery, Lou sends Ferguson on a mission.
episodes.title: Goldfish, Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Wentworth receives a new inmate who knows secrets Reb and Lou are keeping from each other. Allie drugs Ferguson to force her to reveal her true colors.
episodes.title: Monster

episodes.synopsis: Boomer and Gavin meet in person. Lou's cellphone and Reb's surgery money go missing. Ferguson remembers who the little girl in her flashbacks was.
episodes.title: The Enemy Within

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson recovers her memory  and the urge to kill. Allie returns from hospital a changed person. Sheila learns Lou was behind Dr. Mendel's death.
episodes.title: Rogue

episodes.synopsis: Lou sets out to get revenge for Reb. Desperate to get pregnant, Boomer proposes an idea to Gavin. When her dad awakens, Rita makes her peace with him.
episodes.title: Requiem

episodes.synopsis: Lou challenges Boomer to a shiv duel to determine the new top dog. Rita returns to Wentworth. Judy enlists Allie's help in pursuing a legal loophole.
episodes.title: The Ties That Bind

episodes.synopsis: The arrival of an inmate from Ferguson's days as a guard at Blackmoore pushes Joan's buttons. During a dentist visit, Allie learns a useful fact.
episodes.title: Judas Kiss

episodes.synopsis: Allie homes in on her target. Vera notices how chummy Ferguson and Eve have become, and decides to do some investigating on them.
episodes.title: The Unknown Terrorist

episodes.synopsis: Ferguson feeds Eve's delusions about Jake. Rita makes progress in building a case against Jones. Lou helps Judy with her plan but has a secret agenda.
episodes.title: One Eye Open

episodes.synopsis: Marie tells Rita that Lou is planning something big. Vera and Will ask Allie to help them discredit Dr. Miller. Boomer makes progress with Gavin.
episodes.title: Collateral

episodes.synopsis: Rita's efforts to gather evidence against Jones backfire. Vera learns Kath Maxwell's passport was found with one for Grace Maxwell. Boomer takes a test.
episodes.title: The Abyss

episodes.synopsis: With Rita's secret made public, her friends and sister are forced to choose sides. Ferguson's trial begins. Judy gets a surprise visit from her father.
episodes.title: The Reckoning

episodes.synopsis: Boomer makes contact with Gavin. Frazer arrives at Wentworth with the bomb. Allie takes a risk to recover the phone that can exonerate Rita and Ruby.
episodes.title: Legacy
